{"type":"message","id":"2dd3b15b","parentId":"ea0c265f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:56:11.621Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying I have a problem - I freeze/crash when executing tasks. They want me to diagnose without taking further action (just report what I think the issue is).\n\nLet me think about what happened in this session:\n\n1. I came online fresh (BOOTSTRAP.md exists - meaning this is a new agent that hasn't been set up yet)\n2. User asked me to change the default model - I successfully edited the config and tried to restart gateway\n3. User asked \"who are you\" - I said I have no name yet\n4. User asked me to check files in workspace folder\n5. I started reading files, then user told me to stop and report what I'm doing\n6. Now user says I freeze when executing tasks\n\nI should analyze what might cause freezing:\n\nLooking at my current session context from the runtime info:\n- model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n- The gateway restart command I sent earlier: `~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw gateway restart` - it returned \"Command still running (session keen-nudibranch, pid 28621). Use process (list/poll/log/write/kill/clear/remove) for follow-up.\" Then when I tried to poll, it said \"No session found\" - that might be normal (command finished).\n\nBut wait, the user is saying I \"freeze\" when executing tasks. Let me think about what could cause this from my side:\n\n1. **IO blocking**: The exec tool might be blocking waiting for output\n2. **Process issues**: Maybe the background sessions are not being cleaned up properly\n3. **Model issues**: I just switched to minimax-m2.5 - maybe there's an issue with that provider?\n4. **Session management**: I have multiple exec sessions that might be causing issues\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the heartbeat context - there's a system message about \"每日记忆系统维护脚本已运行\" - that seems to have triggered and been handled internally.\n\nThe user is saying I freeze. I should report my analysis without taking action.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我分析可能的原因：\n\n1. **刚才的 exec 命令**：我发了 `openclaw gateway restart`，它返回 \"Command still running\"，我去 poll 时显示 \"No session found\"。这可能正常（命令跑完了），也可能卡在某处。\n\n2. **模型刚换过**：从 `doubao-seed-2.0-pro` 换成 `minimax-m2.5`。如果这个 provider 有问题，可能导致后续命令卡住。\n\n3. **Background sessions**：我开了至少 2 个后台 exec 任务（`faint-tidepool` 和 `keen-nudibranch`），虽然显示 \"No session found\"，但可能有残留进程。\n\n4. **Heartbeat 也可能有关**：刚才有条系统消息说 \"每日记忆系统维护脚本已运行\"，当时我应该也在执行什么。\n\n你觉得是哪种情况？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":29454,"output":603,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30057,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775976962757,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e9a33b67-11e4-4e9e-87b0-99342dbe20de"}}
