{"type":"message","id":"e690a1dd","parentId":"97493c07","timestamp":"2026-04-12T06:58:05.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to think about why the task execution is freezing/cached and report my analysis without taking any actions. Let me think through this carefully.\n\nLet me analyze what's happening:\n\n1. **Recent changes I made**:\n   - Changed default model from `volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro` to `codingplan/minimax-m2.5` in `/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n   - Tried to restart gateway with `openclaw gateway restart`\n\n2. **What could be causing the freeze**:\n\n   a) **Model change issue**: \n      - The new model `codingplan/minimax-m2.5` connects to `https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding/v1`\n      - This endpoint might be slow, unreachable, or returning errors\n      - The model might be timing out\n\n   b) **Gateway restart**:\n      - The command might have partially succeeded or failed\n      - Gateway might be in an inconsistent state\n      - The \"Command still running\" then \"No session found\" suggests the command finished but maybe not cleanly\n\n   c) **Exec sessions**:\n      - I created background sessions that might be stuck\n      - Even though they show \"No session found\", there could be zombie processes\n\n   d) **Provider connectivity**:\n      - The CodingPlan endpoint might have issues\n      - Network latency from WSL2 to that endpoint\n      - API key might have issues\n\n   e) **Configuration**:\n      - The config change might not have been applied correctly\n      - There could be a syntax error in the JSON I edited (though edit said it succeeded)\n\nLet me think about what evidence I have:\n- The exec commands did return outputs, so not completely frozen\n- The edit to openclaw.json succeeded\n- The gateway restart showed \"No session found\" which is weird but could mean it finished\n\nActually wait - the user said \"任务执行一会就卡死了\" - task execution freezes after a while. This could be:\n\n\n- API calls getting stuck because the model provider is slow or unresponsive\n- Background exec sessions that didn't properly terminate\n- The model change introducing latency that compounds over time\n\nI should report this analysis to the user without taking any further action.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，我仔细想：\n\n**最可能的原因：模型 provider 有问题**\n\n我刚把默认模型换成 `codingplan/minimax-m2.5`，它连的是：\n```\nhttps://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding/v1\n```\n\n这个 endpoint 我不了解。可能：\n- 响应慢\n- 网络不通（WSL2 -> 那个域名）\n- API key 不对或过期\n- 直接挂了\n\n**如果连不上，每次我调用模型时就会卡住。**\n\n---\n\n**另一个可能：Gateway 没完全重启成功**\n\n我发了 `openclaw gateway restart`，它返回 \"No session found\"。这可能是：\n- 重启失败了\n- 或部分成功，新旧状态混杂\n\n---\n\n**建议排查方向：**\n\n1. 先确认 `codingplan/minimax-m2.5` 这个 provider 能不能正常调用\n2. 或者先把默认模型改回 `doubao-seed-2.0-pro`，看还卡不卡\n\n你觉得呢？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":29696,"output":680,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30376,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775977071826,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e31d500d-6d34-406d-9b04-6cadc5072fe5"}}
