{"type":"message","id":"809925af","parentId":"ce5c6fe1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T08:48:40.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to check what's wrong, and tell them what I'm going to do before doing it. Let me analyze what could be causing issues:\n\n1. Model provider configuration - I changed the default model to codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n2. The config file might have been corrupted when I edited it\n3. There might be issues with the exec tool returning garbage\n\nLet me check:\n1. The current config file status\n2. Model providers status\n3. Any processes that might be stuck\n\nI should check these things systematically without acting yet, then报告给用户，让他们告诉我下一步怎么做。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，我检查一下：\n\n**1. 配置文件状态**\n\n刚才我用 edit 改过 `openclaw.json` 的默认模型，后来执行 `openclaw gateway restart` 时显示 \"No session found\"，可能没成功。\n\n**2. 模型 Provider 状态**\n\n现在有几个 provider：\n- `volcengine-plan` (默认的豆包)\n- `codingplan` (我刚换成默认的)\n- `deepseek`\n- `ollama`\n\n不确定 `codingplan` 这个 provider 能不能正常连接。\n\n**3. Exec 工具异常**\n\n之前所有 exec 命令返回值都带乱码，可能是：\n- 命令执行过程中出了问题\n- 或者返回格式被污染了\n\n---\n\n**我想做的事情：**\n\n1. 先用 `openclaw status` 确认当前系统状态\n2. 看_default 模型到底改成没\n3. 如果配置有问题，先恢复备份或手动修复\n\n你觉得要继续吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":64035,"output":310,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65497,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775983700123,"responseId":"019d80e0a2fa5d11606656f90d26e420"}}
